{"word":"G5419 - φράζω - phrázō - frad'-zo - Declare","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φράζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phrázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">frad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Declare</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெளிப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to indicate plainly, make known, declare"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G5420 - φράσσω - phrássō - fras'-so/5420\">G5420</a> through the idea of <i>defining</i>; to <i>indicate</i> (by word or act), that is, (specifically) to <i>expound:</i> - declare.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}